    type: 3}
  possible_pos:
  - {fileID: 551834833}
  - {fileID: 551834832}
  - {fileID: 551834831}
  possible_text_popUp:
  - I' dont want to be seen
  - Talking to people makes me shake.
  - My heart races whenever Im near strangers
  - "I don\u2019t know how to handle this..."
  - I want to be at home...
  - Why are they looking at me?
  - "Please don\u2019t notice me!"
  - Why are there so many people here?
  - "My hands won\u2019t stop shaking."
  - "I can\u2019t breathe..."
  - My hands shake whenever I talk to someone..
  - This is too overwhelming.
  - "Do they know I\u2019m scared?"
